View Sample

Sample landing page presents aggregated information about specific sample details and properties, related objects and static text. The sample landing page is divided into tabs that contains specific information.

Sample Header

Sample header contains following information:

  1. Sub-classification of the sample (if it is Sample-Commercial or Sample-Art Object)
  2. State - current sample state
  3. Title of the sample

Sample Dashboard

The dashboard contains aggregated information about specific sample details and properties, related objects and static text

Once the sample is opened, the Sample Dashboard is displayed. Following information is displayed:

  1. Sample data
  2. Sample taken from cultural ob​​​ject
  3. Ongoing activities
  4. Images 
  5. Documents and media
  6. Related Comments 

To access more detailed information select from following tabs:

  1. Details - displays the Sample data
  2. Media - displays all of the related media
  3. Activities - displays all the related activities
  4. System data - to check system data related to the Sample
  5. Permissions - to check the applied permissions on the Sample
  6. ​​​​​​Versions -  display all of the versions of this object
